WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.131
The unanimous advice from our highest-performing sellers is to explore

00:00:04.131 --> 00:00:08.263
this partnership angle aggressively and as early as possible in

00:00:08.263 --> 00:00:12.394
the lifecycle of any high-value strategic opportunity. Remember, cloud representatives

00:00:12.394 --> 00:00:16.526
are brilliant and highly technical, but they are rarely marketing-savvy.

00:00:16.526 --> 00:00:20.657
You must actively pitch them on the mechanics of the

00:00:20.657 --> 00:00:24.789
deal, ask probing questions to unlock high-value visibility into their

00:00:24.789 --> 00:00:28.920
internal portfolio planning, and fiercely garner their direct support.
